value.name: 35 (number) - Wikipedia
value.snippet: 35 is the number of ways that three things can be selected from a set of seven unique things, also known as the "combination of seven things taken three at a time". 35 is a centered cube number , [2] a centered tetrahedral number , a pentagonal number , [3] and a pentatope number .
